{"id":"6758","name":"happy-hour-it-must-be-food-truck-day","title":"Happy Hour: It Must Be Food Truck Day","author":"Christy Frink","date":"2011-03-29T17:30:00-05:00","tags":["christian siriano","confederate flag","earthquake","japan","metro public works","nashville cherry blossom festival","nashville fashion week","redistricting","shelby street bridge","tin pan south","tsunami","wine in grocery stores"],"categories":["News"],"contentEncoded":"<div id=\"greet_block\"><noscript><div class=\"greet_block wpgb_cornered\"><div class=\"greet_text\"><div class=\"greet_image\"><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/feed/rss/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"http://nashvillest.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-greet-box/images/rss_icon.png\" alt=\"WP Greet Box icon\"></a></div>Hello there! If you&apos;re new to Nashvillest, you might want to <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/nashvillest\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>subscribe to our RSS feed</strong></a> to make sure you don&apos;t miss anything! We&apos;re also on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/nashvillest\" target=\"blank\"><strong>Twitter</strong></a> if you&apos;d like to join us there!<div style=\"clear:both\"></div><div class=\"greet_block_powered_by\">Powered by <a href=\"http://omninoggin.com/projects/wordpress-plugins/wp-greet-box-wordpress-plugin/\" title=\"WP Greet Box WordPress Plugin\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">WP Greet Box</a> <a href=\"http://omninoggin.com/\" title=\"WordPress Plugin\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">WordPress Plugin</a></div><div style=\"clear:both\"></div></div></div></noscript></div><p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/ruuustin/5540382697/in/pool-715021@N24/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.flickr.com&apos;]);\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://farm6.static.flickr.com/5135/5540382697_70bcc95a8a.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\"></a></p><ul><li>A measure that would allow wine to be shipped directly to any house in Tennessee has at least passed the state Senate. So if we can&#x2019;t buy it in grocery stores, at least we may be able to have it delivered to our front doors. [<a href=\"http://www.newschannel5.com/story/14338092/bill-to-allow-direct-shipment-of-wine-in-tennessee\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.newschannel5.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">WTVF</a>]</li><li>That other bill allowing supermarkets to actually sell wine was delayed in a Senate committee today after a colorful debate about how it might affect liquor stores. Supporters took the opportunity to point out that it could generate as much as $14 million in extra tax revenue for both the state and its localities. [<a href=\"http://www.newschannel5.com/story/14342929/wine-in-supermarkets-bill-delayed-in-senate-panel\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.newschannel5.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">WTVF</a>]</li><li>Metro is still going back and forth on the redistricting process, and not everyone is pleased with it. [<a href=\"http://nashvillecitypaper.com/content/city-news/reactions-mixed-planning-departments-redistricting-map\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;nashvillecitypaper.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">City Paper</a>]</li><li>Someone decided to hang a confederate flag from the Shelby Street Bridge this morning, which is apparently not such a rare occurrence. Folks noticed quickly and the flag was removed by Metro Public Works. [<a href=\"http://nashvillecitypaper.com/content/city-news/city-remove-confederate-flag-hanging-pedestrian-bridge?utm_source=feedburner&amp;utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+NashvilleCityPaper-LatestNews+%28Nashville+City+Paper+-+Latest+News%29\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;nashvillecitypaper.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">City Paper</a>]</li><li>Well done, Nashville! You raised more than $50,000 for Japan disaster relief at last weekend&#x2019;s Cherry Blossom Festival. [<a href=\"http://www.newschannel5.com/story/14344137/nearly-52000-raised-at-cherry-blossom-festival\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.newschannel5.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">WTVF</a>]</li><li>If Nashville&#x2019;s looking a bit more fashionable this week, it&#x2019;s because our very first <a href=\"http://nashvillefashionweek.com/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;nashvillefashionweek.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Lexus Nashville Fashion Week</a> kicked off today and runs through Saturday. Project Runway&#x2019;s Christian Siriano will be in town along with a whole slew of other designers from near and far. Check out the website for the schedule and details. [<a href=\"http://www.wkrn.com/story/14337309/nashville-hosts-first-ever-fashion-week\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wkrn.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">WKRN</a>]</li><li>Also, <a href=\"http://www.tinpansouth.com/welcome.html\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.tinpansouth.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Tin Pan South</a> got off to a great start today, featuring some of the best songwriters from all over the country. Check their website for the rest of the lowdown. [<a href=\"http://www.wsmv.com/entertainment/27355489/detail.html\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wsmv.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">WSMV</a>]</li></ul><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><em>Photo by <a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/ruuustin/5540382697/in/pool-715021@N24/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.flickr.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Dustin Rumbaugh</a></em>.</p><p>Related posts:<ol><li><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2011/02/15/things-we-like-nashvilles-first-food-truck-food-court/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link: Things We Like: Nashville&#x2019;s First Food Truck Food Court\">Things We Like: Nashville&#x2019;s First Food Truck Food Court</a></li><li><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2011/05/27/happy-eating-happy-japan-debuts-japanese-food-truck-tonight-in-five-points/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link: Happy Eating: Happy Japan Debuts Japanese Food Truck Tonight In Five Points\">Happy Eating: Happy Japan Debuts Japanese Food Truck Tonight In Five Points</a></li></ol></p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<!--END .entry-content .article-->"}